---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="扩展市场 - BangNiCMS"
  description="浏览、试用、一键安装由社区与官方维护的 BangNiCMS 主题与插件"
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <span
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-amber-800 dark:border-amber-900/50 dark:bg-amber-950/50 dark:text-amber-300"
      >
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-amber-400 opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500"></span>
        </span>
        即将上线
      </span>

      <h1
        class="mt-6 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl dark:text-white"
      >
        扩展市场
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        浏览、试用并一键安装由社区与官方维护的<strong class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">主题</strong>与<strong class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">插件</strong>，让你的站点几分钟内焕然一新。
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 text-left dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-slate-900/50"
        >
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">10+</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">官方主题</div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 text-left dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-slate-900/50"
        >
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">20+</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">实用插件</div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 text-left dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-slate-900/50"
        >
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">100%</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">兼容当前版本</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-12 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500">
        我们正在打磨这个市场。到时这里会有完整的浏览、详情、安装命令复制。
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-md bg-slate-900 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-all hover:bg-slate-800 dark:bg-white dark:text-slate-900 dark:hover:bg-slate-200"
        >
          返回首页
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/docs/getting-started/installation"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-transparent dark:text-slate-200 dark:hover:bg-white/5"
        >
          阅读文档
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>
